        <ol>
          <li>Storage Wars:</li>
          <ol>
            <li>Reality show:  Real people with differing, but interesting, personalities.</li>
            <li>Simple concept:  Not difficult to understand what there doing and to feel that you could do it too.</li>
            <li>Challenge:  Price is right style challenge of guessing what the locker is worth.</li>
            <li>Gambling:  Each locker auction is basically a gamble and the show portrays the gambling process with results very well.</li>
            <li>Artifacts:  The gambling factor builds excitement but it's the artifacts and their real-world appraisals and history that really hooks the viewer.</li>
            <li>What it's missing:  Although a very addicting show to start, looses it's appeal after a season because it lacks depth - the personalities and
